    "title": "A great stay thanks to a TOP organization!",
    "rating": 5,
    "travelDate": "2023-11",
    "publishedDate": "2023-12-15",
    "text": "Thanks to their experiences, their perfect knowledge and their empathy for Africa, Julie and Vincent were able to organize for us an exceptional and unforgettable SelfDrive trip of more than 3 weeks to discover Botswana, Zimbabwe, Zambia and the Caprivi Strip. Nickel on everything: the organization, the rhythm, the circuit, the routes, the choice of accommodation alternating between Campsites (exceptional for contact with animals), Lodges and Hotels, their advice, their availability, their attention.\nThanking you once again, Julie and Vincent for this stay which will remain engraved in our memories.\nAnnie and Philippe",
